       </p>
       <p>
        Support for this series is provided by Dr. and Mrs. Tom Colby, the Library, The Morrison Library Fund, the dean's office of the College of Letters and Sciences, the English Department, and the Townsend Center for the Humanities. These events are also partially supported by Poets &amp; Writers, Inc. through a grant it has received from The James Irvine Foundation.
       </p>
